Interface Indexed<T>

  • Type Parameters:
    T -
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    JImmutableArray<T>, JImmutableList<T>, JImmutableRandomAccessList<T>
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractJImmutableArray, Bit32Array, EmptyBit32Array, FullBit32Array, IndexedArray, IndexedList, JImmutableArrayList, JImmutableBtreeList, JImmutableTreeList, SingleBit32Array, StandardBit32Array, Subindexed, TrieArray

    public interface Indexed<T>
    Interface for containers that allow access to values by an integer index.
